{"pageid":28395,"pagename":"Champion's scroll","title":"Champion's scroll","displaytitle":"Champion's scroll","revid":14271566,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Champion's scrolls are scrolls that players can obtain when killing certain monsters. It is a challenge from that creature's race champion, and by taking the scroll to the cellar of the Champions' Guild, they may be fought in the Champion's Challenge minigame. Each scroll is an extremely rare (1 in 5,000) drop from monsters of each race. When one is received as a drop, the message, \"A Champion's scroll falls to the ground as you slay your opponent,\" appears. In order to be eligible to receive any Champion's scroll, players must have 32 quest points and be on a members world.&#91;1&#93;"}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Champion&#39;s scroll.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Champion%27s_scroll\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Champion&#39;s scroll\">rsw:Champion's scroll</a></span></div>\n<p><b>Champion's scrolls</b> are scrolls that players can obtain when killing certain monsters. It is a challenge from that creature's race champion, and by taking the scroll to the cellar of the <a href=\"/w/Champions%27_Guild\" title=\"Champions&#39; Guild\">Champions' Guild</a>, they may be fought in the <a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_Challenge\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Champion&#39;s Challenge\">Champion's Challenge</a> <a href=\"/w/Minigame\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Minigame\">minigame</a>. Each scroll is an extremely rare (1 in 5,000) drop from monsters of each race. When one is received as a drop, the message, \"<i>A Champion's scroll falls to the ground as you slay your opponent,\"</i> appears. In order to be eligible to receive any Champion's scroll, players must have 32 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">quest points</a> and be on a <a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">members</a> world.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Every champion has certain rules that the battle is fought under. These are outlined on the scroll. After winning the battle with the champion, players will get a small amount of <a href=\"/w/Experience\" title=\"Experience\">experience</a> in <a href=\"/w/Hitpoints\" title=\"Hitpoints\">Hitpoints</a> and <a href=\"/w/Slayer\" title=\"Slayer\">Slayer</a> <a href=\"/w/Skill\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skill\">skills</a>, and you cannot obtain another champion's scroll of that type again.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Although you cannot receive the Champion's scroll after completing the challenge, it is possible to roll the drop again in which case you will receive the message \"<i>You have a funny feeling you would have received a Champion's scroll...</i>\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>There are 10 different champion scrolls, each from a different race's champion, plus 1 champion scroll from champion of champions, human race champion <a href=\"/w/Leon_D%27Cour\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Leon D&#39;Cour\">Leon D'Cour</a>, who can only be fought after beating all other champions. When every champion has been slain, you may claim the <a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_cape\" title=\"Champion&#39;s cape\">Champion's cape</a> from <a href=\"/w/Larxus\" title=\"Larxus\">Larxus</a>.\n</p><p>A champion's scroll is needed for the <a href=\"/w/Music_cape\" title=\"Music cape\">music cape</a>, as the soundtrack \"<a href=\"/w/Victory_is_Mine\" title=\"Victory is Mine\">Victory is Mine</a>\" is unlocked in the arena.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Scrolls\">Scrolls</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_scroll?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Scrolls\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_scroll?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Scrolls\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable lighttable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Scroll</th>\n<th>Dropping <a href=\"/w/Monster\" title=\"Monster\">monster</a> (<a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">level</a>)</th>\n<th>Champion (<a href=\"/w/Combat_level\" title=\"Combat level\">level</a>)\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Imp_champion_scroll\" title=\"Imp champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Imp champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Imp_champion_scroll.png?f36f9\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Imp_champion_scroll\" title=\"Imp champion scroll\">Imp</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Imp\" title=\"Imp\">Imp</a> (2, 7)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Imp_Champion\" title=\"Imp Champion\">Imp Champion</a> (14)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Goblin_champion_scroll\" title=\"Goblin champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Goblin champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Goblin_champion_scroll.png?923a0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Goblin_champion_scroll\" title=\"Goblin champion scroll\">Goblin</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Goblin\" title=\"Goblin\">Goblin</a> (2-13)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Goblin_Champion\" title=\"Goblin Champion\">Goblin Champion</a> (24)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Skeleton_champion_scroll\" title=\"Skeleton champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Skeleton champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Skeleton_champion_scroll.png?1d1f2\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Skeleton_champion_scroll\" title=\"Skeleton champion scroll\">Skeleton</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Skeleton\" title=\"Skeleton\">Skeleton</a> (13-142)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Skeleton_Champion\" title=\"Skeleton Champion\">Skeleton Champion</a> (40)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Zombie_champion_scroll\" title=\"Zombie champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Zombie champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Zombie_champion_scroll.png?37c64\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Zombie_champion_scroll\" title=\"Zombie champion scroll\">Zombie</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Zombie\" title=\"Zombie\">Zombie</a> (13-100)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Zombies_Champion\" title=\"Zombies Champion\">Zombies Champion</a> (51)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Giant_champion_scroll\" title=\"Giant champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Giant champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Giant_champion_scroll.png?06540\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Giant_champion_scroll\" title=\"Giant champion scroll\">Giant</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Hill_giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hill giant\">Hill giant</a> (28), <a href=\"/w/Fire_Giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fire Giant\">Fire Giant</a>, <a href=\"/w/Moss_Giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Moss Giant\">Moss Giant</a>, <a href=\"/w/Ice_giant\" title=\"Ice giant\">Ice giant</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Giant_Champion\" title=\"Giant Champion\">Giant Champion</a> (56)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Hobgoblin_champion_scroll\" title=\"Hobgoblin champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Hobgoblin champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Hobgoblin_champion_scroll.png?53fc0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Hobgoblin_champion_scroll\" title=\"Hobgoblin champion scroll\">Hobgoblin</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Hobgoblin\" title=\"Hobgoblin\">Hobgoblin</a> (28, 42)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Hobgoblin_Champion\" title=\"Hobgoblin Champion\">Hobgoblin Champion</a> (56)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Ghoul_champion_scroll\" title=\"Ghoul champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Ghoul champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Ghoul_champion_scroll.png?d2266\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Ghoul_champion_scroll\" title=\"Ghoul champion scroll\">Ghoul</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Ghoul\" title=\"Ghoul\">Ghoul</a> (42)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Ghoul_Champion\" title=\"Ghoul Champion\">Ghoul Champion</a> (85)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Earth_warrior_champion_scroll\" title=\"Earth warrior champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Earth warrior champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Earth_warrior_champion_scroll.png?0a875\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Earth_warrior_champion_scroll\" title=\"Earth warrior champion scroll\">Earth warrior</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Earth_warrior\" title=\"Earth warrior\">Earth warrior</a> (51)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Earth_Warrior_Champion\" title=\"Earth Warrior Champion\">Earth Warrior Champion</a> (102)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Jogre_champion_scroll\" title=\"Jogre champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Jogre champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Jogre_champion_scroll.png?be618\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Jogre_champion_scroll\" title=\"Jogre champion scroll\">Jogre</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Jogre\" title=\"Jogre\">Jogre</a> (53)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Jogre_Champion\" title=\"Jogre Champion\">Jogre Champion</a> (107)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Lesser_demon_champion_scroll\" title=\"Lesser demon champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Lesser demon champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Lesser_demon_champion_scroll.png?a6990\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Lesser_demon_champion_scroll\" title=\"Lesser demon champion scroll\">Lesser demon</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Lesser_demon\" title=\"Lesser demon\">Lesser demon</a> (82, 87, 94)</td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Lesser_Demon_Champion\" title=\"Lesser Demon Champion\">Lesser Demon Champion</a> (162)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Leon%27s_champion_scroll\" title=\"Leon&#39;s champion scroll\"><img alt=\"Leon&#39;s champion scroll.png\" src=\"/images/Leon%27s_champion_scroll.png?a6990\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Leon%27s_champion_scroll\" title=\"Leon&#39;s champion scroll\">Human</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Unobtainable_items\" title=\"Unobtainable items\">Unobtainable</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Leon_d%27Cour\" title=\"Leon d&#39;Cour\">Leon d'Cour</a> (141)\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_scroll?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_scroll?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th>Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/16_December\" title=\"16 December\">16&#160;December</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Christmas_2021\" title=\"Update:Christmas 2021\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>If a Champion's scroll would have dropped as a duplicate, the game message \"<i><span style=\"color:#990000;\">You have a funny feeling that you would have received a Champion's scroll...</span></i>\" appears now.\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/25_June\" title=\"25 June\">25&#160;June</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2015\" title=\"2015\">2015</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Boss_Room_Counters_%26_Platinum_Tokens\" title=\"Update:Boss Room Counters &amp; Platinum Tokens\">update</a>&#160;|&#160;<a href=\"/w/Poll:Old_School_Content_Poll_34:_XP_droplets_%26_Slayer\" title=\"Poll:Old School Content Poll 34: XP droplets &amp; Slayer\">poll</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Players will now receive a coloured message in their chat box upon receiving a champion scroll drop.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_scroll?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Champion%27s_scroll?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small hideQuotes\"><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jagex. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.is/9KMB5\">Mod Ash's Twitter account</a>. 14 January 2019.  (Archived from <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1084801603281002496\">the original</a> on 26 May 2020.) Mod Ash: \"The Champions Challenge? You need 32+ QP, and to be on a members' world.\" </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jagex. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.is/K97dq\">Mod Ash's Twitter account</a>. 18 April 2019.  (Archived from <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1118793092440764416\">the original</a> on 26 May 2020.) Mod Ash: \"If you've killed a specific champion, the game no longer drops its challenge scroll for you.\" </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jagex. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.ph/LZanp\">Mod Ash's Twitter account</a>. 16 December 2021.  (Archived from <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1471450361030483973\">the original</a> on 8 April 2022.) Mod Ash: \"Yes, we added a message if you roll the random number but don't receive a scroll because you'd already done the challenge. Someone suggested they'd like to know, so their clan could use it for bingo.\" </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Champions\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Champions\" title=\"Template:Champions\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Champions\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Champions?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Champions%27_Challenge\" title=\"Champions&#39; Challenge\">Champions' Challenge</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Lower Champions</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Earth_Warrior_Champion\" title=\"Earth Warrior Champion\">Earth Warrior</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ghoul_Champion\" title=\"Ghoul Champion\">Ghoul</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Giant_Champion\" title=\"Giant Champion\">Giant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Goblin_Champion\" title=\"Goblin Champion\">Goblin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Hobgoblin_Champion\" title=\"Hobgoblin Champion\">Hobgoblin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Imp_Champion\" title=\"Imp Champion\">Imp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Jogre_Champion\" title=\"Jogre Champion\">Jogre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Lesser_Demon_Champion\" title=\"Lesser Demon Champion\">Lesser Demon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Skeleton_Champion\" title=\"Skeleton Champion\">Skeleton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Zombies_Champion\" title=\"Zombies Champion\">Zombie</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Champion of Champions</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Leon_d%27Cour\" title=\"Leon d&#39;Cour\"><img alt=\"Leon d&#39;Cour chathead.png: Chat head image of L